WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.260 --> 00:00:11.580
Oh.

2
00:00:14.390 --> 00:00:23.919
Woo-hoo!

3
00:00:24.270 --> 00:00:25.480
Huh?

4
00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:42.000
Woo! Woo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

5
00:00:56.980 --> 00:01:01.460
Why? Ah, Dr. Zoidberg. Hooray

6
00:01:01.560 --> 00:01:03.290
for Dr. Zoidberg.

7
00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:59.700
Eh? Eh?

8
00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:58.360
Tell everybody I'm on my way. New friends

9
00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:02.920
and new places to see. With blue

10
00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:07.820
skies ahead, yes, I'm on my way. And there's nowhere

11
00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:12.840
else that I'd rather be. Oh, tell

12
00:03:12.860 --> 00:03:17.540
everybody I'm on my way. And I'm loving

13
00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.720
every step I take.
